    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172900/extras/f49d51ef6f51610abdba2877acd7441f.poster.avif?t=1749373752\" width=628 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172900/extras/f49d51ef6f51610abdba2877acd7441f.webm?t=1749373752\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172900/extras/f49d51ef6f51610abdba2877acd7441f.mp4?t=1749373752\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >控制混沌领主的军队，指挥飞行堡垒，招募和升级你的部队，探索充满挑战的奇幻世界。试玩版包括战役中的部分任务，让您体验这款激动人心的续作的游戏玩法和机制。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>演示版的主要功能</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有限的战役任务让你体验故事情节。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用选定的单位和能力，尝试不同的战术。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索新游戏增强的视觉效果和动画效果</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172900/extras/4989ad5d5f235c4265c2abb6a9e90936.poster.avif?t=1749373752\" width=628 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172900/extras/4989ad5d5f235c4265c2abb6a9e90936.webm?t=1749373752\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172900/extras/4989ad5d5f235c4265c2abb6a9e90936.mp4?t=1749373752\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>故事</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >奥勒留国王不幸去世后，大主教马里乌斯找到上古亡灵领主，希望与他们达成交易。在诱惑之下，马略计划获得一件能够赋予宗教裁判所无限力量的神器。作为回报，他将帮助领主们夺取梦寐以求的水之神殿。亡灵领主接受了这笔交易，于是混沌领主加入了游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您可以招募拥有多种技能和武器偏好的新战士，创建一支独一无二的小队。分配给您的任务不仅需要勇士们的力量，还需要他们的狡猾。寻找珍贵文物、突袭城市、征服敌方指挥官、亵渎土地和占领祭坛只是您将面临的部分挑战。</p>",
